      ],
      "uco-core:name": "Teixeira destroys iPad and desktop computer",
      "uco-core:description": "Destroyed his electronic devices, including his desktop computer and iPad, discarding some in a dumpster outside his home; the iPad was found smashed. Source: PACER Doc 144 (sentencing_memorandum), p. 8",
