      ],
      "uco-core:name": "Indictment, Doc 48 (filed 2023-06-15)",
      "legalproc:instrumentType": "indictment",
      "uco-core:description": "Six counts of Willful Retention and Transmission of National Defense Information (18 U.S.C. \u00a7 793(e)) plus a forfeiture allegation (18 U.S.C. \u00a7\u00a7 981(a)(1)(C), 793(h); 28 U.S.C. \u00a7 2461(c)). The sentencing memorandum describes the grand jury as returning the indictment in May 2023; the filed document is stamped 2023-06-15. Source: PACER Doc 48 (indictment), caption"
    },
