      "uco-core:description": "Charges that Jan. 2023 to April 2023, having unauthorized possession of, access to, and control over documents relating to the national defense, Teixeira willfully communicated, delivered, and transmitted it to persons not entitled to receive it and willfully retained it. Charged NDI (TOP SECRET//SCI): A Government Document that describes a shift in foreign and economic policy of a particular foreign government and actions that country took in an effort to repair its relationship with the United States, to the perceived detriment of a separate foreign country. Source: PACER Doc 48 (indictment), paras. 15-18"
